---
title: Smart Provençal-Style Shrimp Stew with Zesty Garlic Aioli
description: This comforting stew, deeply flavoured with aromatics and sweetened with tomatoes, gets a zesty pick-me-up from lemon. A dollop of garlicky aioli adds a hint of creaminess that makes this dinner unforgettable!

